contentfulBlogPost.title: From Developer Full Time Into Freelancer  and finally on path to move beyond

content.value: From Developer full time into freelance and beyond

It was a tough, challenging journey when I started, but with time things started becoming easier for me. I started getting new opportunities every day. And now things are getting too overwhelming, I have literally filled my time with work. For the past two months I have been working every day including weekends that's from 9:00 am to 9:30 pm.
So I feel its right time to move forward and start owning your own business so that you can divide the work between your team. Will keep updated on my progress.
